data.description: Take a look at this beautiful Northwest home in the Calloway Country neighborhood. This home features 4 bedrooms, 3 baths, new wood flooring, formal living and dining, family room, large kitchen with granite counters and a large breakfast nook. Home is walking distance from schools, shopping centers and restaurants! The backyard has plenty of patio space with a POOL, perfect for entertaining and for those hot summer days! Must see to appreciate. Don't miss the opportunity to make this home your own. Call to schedule your showing today!
